title: G4 Hurl Episodes 4, 5 & 8
description:
104:
Five contestants eat broccoli and cauliflower with cheese sauce before riding on the "Octopus."

105:
In honor of the 2008 Summer Olympics in China, the contestants eat Chinese food before riding a roller coaster.

108:
The contestants must face a challenging ride on a mechanical bull after eating not-so-solid foods.

Note: G4TechTV has been airing this show out of order and sometimes the same episode will air 2 weeks in a row.
